  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q87",
  "body": "What is repentance unto life?\n\nRepentance unto life is a saving grace, whereby a sinner, out of a true sense of his sin, and apprehension of the mercy of God in Christ, doth, with grief and hatred of his sin, turn from it unto God, with full purpose of, and endeavor after, new obedience.",
